# Title: AspNetCompiler Execution
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2021-11-24
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects execution of "aspnet_compiler.exe" which can be abused to compile and execute C# code.
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.stealth, attack.t1127
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_aspnet_compiler_exectuion.yml

Image IN ("*:\\Windows\\Microsoft.NET\\Framework\\*", "*:\\Windows\\Microsoft.NET\\Framework64\\*", "*:\\Windows\\Microsoft.NET\\FrameworkArm\\*", "*:\\Windows\\Microsoft.NET\\FrameworkArm64\\*") Image="*\\aspnet_compiler.exe"